Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest queue resume

Purpose:
  Requeue one paused job.

Usage:
  spinedigest queue resume <job-id>

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Behavior:
  - Resume changes the job back to queued.
  - The transient worker is started if needed.

Example:
  spinedigest queue resume 75d12f7e
